==Lap records==

The total length of the circuit is , which is about average for a Formula One circuit. Michael Schumacher&#x27;s official race lap record of 1:32.238 has stood since 2004. In Q3 of 2018 Chinese Grand Prix, Sebastian Vettel qualified on pole position with a time of 1:31.095, a new unofficial track record. As of September 2024, the fastest official race lap records at the Shanghai International Circuit are listed as:

